original_text: The Lord bringeth the counsel of the heathen to nought: he maketh the devices of the people of none effect.
korean_text: 여호와께서 나라들의 계획을 폐하시며 민족들의 사상을 무효하게 하시도다

sentences.original_text: The Lord bringeth the counsel of the heathen to nought
he maketh the devices of the people of none effect
